### Create a new cart
POST http://localhost:8080/carts/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### Get all carts
GET http://localhost:8080/carts

### Get a specific cart by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/carts/{id}

### Add item to cart
POST http://localhost:8080/carts/{id}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Update item quantity in cart
PUT http://localhost:8080/carts/{id}/items/{itemId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### Remove item from cart
DELETE http://localhost:8080/carts/{id}/items/{itemId}

### Clear all items from cart
DELETE http://localhost:8080/carts/{id}/items